Honestly it's fine to disagree on the merits of 228 but to call this a VC proposal as an attempt to spread FUD is ridiculous.

Yes Multicoin is a VC, They're the VC that's been all in on Solana since 2018 through good times and bad.

They led the Solana seed round in 2018, when nobody else would.
They led the Solana A in 2019, when nobody else would.
They led the Solana B in 2020, when nobody else would.
They followed on again in 2021, when everyone else wanted in.
And when sol went from all time highs back down to 8$ they held it all because they still believed in Solana when nobody else did. 

Now that that conviction has paid off and they don't need to work a day in their lives anymore Tushar, and Kyle are still in the arena. Whether it's in DC, Park City, NY, SF, or on the Internet, they wake up every day and go to work to ensure Solana wins.

To suggest that this proposal is somehow tainted because people who believe in Solana and want it to succeed this much are involved is absurd.
